{"oid": "eea792a8bb39", "path": "README.md", "size": 1004, "pat": "mnemonic", "line": 11, "text": "The wallet mnemonic was encrypted directly using the pinned `pvac_hfhe_cpp` implementation."}
{"oid": "eea792a8bb39", "path": "README.md", "size": 1004, "pat": "mnemonic", "line": 15, "text": "- `seed.ct`: the encrypted wallet mnemonic"}
{"oid": "eea792a8bb39", "path": "README.md", "size": 1004, "pat": "mnemonic", "line": 22, "text": "There is no passphrase, PBKDF2, AES-GCM, sealed storage envelope, or additional encryption layer protecting the mnemonic."}
{"oid": "eea792a8bb39", "path": "README.md", "size": 1004, "pat": "mnemonic", "line": 26, "text": "The winning condition is simple: recover the mnemonic encrypted in `seed.ct` and use it to submit a valid transaction from the funded wallet before the challenge is withdrawn."}
{"oid": "eea792a8bb39", "path": "README.md", "size": 1004, "pat": "mnemonic", "line": 28, "text": "The secret key and plaintext mnemonic are not published."}
